dcterms:description: A dataset designed for generating Chinese fonts, incorporating stroke information to enhance the generation of complex characters.
dcterms:title: Stroke-aware dataset for Chinese font generation

dcterms:description: A dataset tailored for generating Korean fonts, utilizing component information to improve the generation of intricate characters.
dcterms:title: Component-aware dataset for Korean font generation

dcterms:description: A dataset containing 410 different Chinese fonts, each with 6,625 characters, covering almost all commonly used Chinese characters.
dcterms:title: Chinese font dataset (410 fonts)

dcterms:description: A dataset comprising 201 Korean fonts, each containing a variety of characters for font generation tasks.
dcterms:title: Korean font dataset (201 fonts)
